items.name: NV Packing Station
items.description: Place Element and Trophys in here to package them for transport.

items.name: 2x2 Stone Ceiling
items.description: A stable brick-and-mortar ceiling that insulates the inside from the outside, and doubles as a floor for higher levels.

items.name: 2x2 Wood Ceiling
items.description: A stable brick-and-mortar ceiling that insulates the inside from the outside, and doubles as a floor for higher levels.

items.name: 2x2 Metal Foundation
items.description: A foundation is required to build structures in an area.  This one is made from brick-and-mortar.

items.name: 2x2 Stone Foundation
items.description: A foundation is required to build structures in an area.  This one is made from brick-and-mortar.

items.name: 2x2 Wooden Foundation
items.description: A foundation is required to build structures in an area.  This one is made from sturdy wood.

items.name: NV Converter
items.description: Converts vanilla structures & blueprints to their NV or S+ counterpart and vice versa.

items.name: NV Dedicated Storage Consolidator
items.description:
Will consolidate items from your dinos and storages that have associated nearby dedicated storage units.

Can be upgraded in size. (does not change distribution range)

items.name: NV Fish Basket
items.description: Trap certain fish in this basket to tame and transport them, even across arks!

items.name: Give Structure Campfire
items.description: This composite Tek pillar adds structural integrity to the area it is build under.  Can also act as stilts for buildings on inclines.

items.name: Item Collector
items.description: This composite Tek pillar adds structural integrity to the area it is build under.  Can also act as stilts for buildings on inclines.

items.name: Leech Farm
items.description:
Needs Blood Pack to activate.
Place your leeches inside fence to harvest their blood.

items.name: NV Tek Forcefield
items.description:
Generates an impenetrable, expandable spherical shield.

Public mode: keeps out wild dinos.
Ally mode: only allow alliance members and dinos.
Private mode: only allow tribe members and dinos.

Requires Element or Tek Gen to run.
Max size requires three Tek Gens or only Element.

items.name: Summon Desert Titan
items.description: Use this to summon the Desert Titan.

items.name: Desert Titan Terminal
items.description: Summon Desert Titan here!

items.name: NV WorkBench
items.description: Craft stuff from Norwegian Vikings mod here.

items.name: NV Command Gun
items.description:
Use this to execute commands on your dinos.
Mousewheel changes command.
Rightclick changes mode.

items.name: NV Spray Painter
items.description:
A spray painter that can penetrate world geometry and also doesn't run out of paint.
Apply a dye to this, then shoot it at structures to paint them. Hold Alt Fire + Hotkey Number to set painting region.

items.name: NV Torch
items.description: Provides light, and some warmth. Doubles as a melee weapon in a pinch, and can be applied to various saddles for a mobile light source. Lasts for what feels like an eternity.
